# Seller Business Logic Rules

Seller domain includes:
- networks
- inventory/cards
- sales
- withdrawals
- analytics

Inventory rules:
- cards/packages must maintain consistent state
- prevent duplicate selling
- support reservation lifecycle

Withdrawal rules:
- support request lifecycle
- support status tracking
- maintain transaction traceability

Analytics should include:
- sales totals
- inventory counts
- order statistics
- earnings overview

Avoid:
- mixing seller and admin responsibilities
- bypassing transaction logic
- duplicated financial calculations

Seller logic should remain domain-oriented and reusable.
